---
// Skills section
---

<section id="skills">
  <div class="section-container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">What I do</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Where I tend to<br />make a difference</h2>

    <div class="skills-grid">
      <div class="skill-card reveal">
        <div class="skill-icon">◎</div>
        <h3>Scale engineering teams</h3>
        <p>I build, mentor, and grow high-performing teams. From hiring to coaching,
          I create the structures and culture that let developers do their best work
          while shipping reliably.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="skill-icon">◆</div>
        <h3>Deliver modern web products</h3>
        <p>I turn product requirements into fast, accessible, and maintainable interfaces
          that users love and businesses can iterate on quickly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="skill-icon">⬡</div>
        <h3>De-risk with cloud &amp; automation</h3>
        <p>AWS (certified), Docker, CI/CD pipelines, test automation. I reduce deployment
          friction and infrastructure costs so teams can release with confidence,
          not anxiety.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="skill-icon">⚡</div>
        <h3>Accelerate with AI</h3>
        <p>From AI-powered code review to LLM-driven workflows, I help organisations
          adopt AI pragmatically, boosting developer productivity and reducing
          time-to-market.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <div class="skill-icon">△</div>
        <h3>Bridge product and engineering</h3>
        <p>I translate business goals into technical roadmaps and vice versa. Stakeholder
          alignment, sprint planning, and clear communication keep everyone moving
          in the same direction.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <div class="skill-icon">○</div>
        <h3>Own the full stack</h3>
        <p>When the problem spans frontend to backend to infrastructure, I can assess,
          architect, and execute across the entire stack.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
